  "original_title": "\u0b92\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc7 \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd  - \u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Economic crisis can be solved only by working together - United National Party",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe will present a plan to find a permanent solution to the basic problems in the economic and social structure within the next 06 months.",
        "United National Party Secretary and Member of Parliament Wajira Abeywardhana said that the economic crisis can be solved only if all the people of the country work together.",
        "Commenting on the political and economic situation of the country, he mentioned the above.",
        "Due to various factors, the economic crisis has intensified in the worst way ever in history.",
        "The people of the country know very well who is responsible for the economic crisis. If only allegations are made, the current situation will never be resolved.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe will present a plan to find a sustainable solution to the basic problems in the economy and social structure within the next 06 months.",
        "All the problems can be solved only if all the people of the country work together.",
        "It can be observed that some political parties are acting on the basis of political objective in the background of intensifying economic damage.",
        "It can be observed that certain parties are currently refusing to join the all-party government based on political motives, that they will join the all-party government if former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa resigns.",
        "Our main demand is to hold elections once the economic crisis is solved. The practical problems should be solved.",
        "He said that all the parties should understand how to go to the elections while mentioning that the importation of fuel and essential items for the coming month is difficult."
      ],
